ess of the expedition.&#10;&#10;The Twilight Lab, with its extensive knowledge about the Sun and Mercury, will play a crucial role in helping the Major and his team prepare for the journey and increase their chances of success. The lab is located in a twilight zone between Brightside and Darkside, where temperatures are more survivable, making it an ideal starting point for the expedition.">
